-- China Issues Draft Proposal on State Secrets Law Implementation
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2012-05-15T15:22:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-15/china-issues-draft-proposal-on-state-secrets-law-implementation.html
China issued a draft proposal for a
regulation under the State Secrets Law, according to a document
on the website of the legislative-affairs office of the State
Council.  The proposal defines the scope of state secrets and the
requirements for individuals and organizations involved in
activities deemed confidential, according to the document.  To contact Bloomberg News staff for this story:
William Bi in Beijing at 
 wbi@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
